14. Rac1 (14. Rad1 Rac8 15. Rfe1 Rfe8 16. Bc1 Nd5 17. Bd2 Bf8 $11 {[%cal Yd5b4]
}) 14... Rac8 15. Rfd1 Na5 $11 16. Bb5 Bc6 17. Ba6 Bb7 $11) (6. Bh4 {[%csl Yh4]
the bishop is doing nothing on this diagonal, so Black can play actively in
