proper reply:} Ne4 $1 (5... e6 {is also solid:} 6. e3 Be7 7. Bd3 Nc6 {[%csl
Gc6] If the knight was already on d7 (like in the Orthodox Defence) it would
be misplaced, but since c6 is available here, Black has a good position}) 6.
Nxe4 ({both bishop's retreats are bad:} 6. Bf4 Nc6 7. e3 g5 $1 8. Bg3 h5 9.
